  }, "v19"), mdx("p", null, "Khi c\xE1c ng\u01B0\u01A1i \u0111\u1EBFn g\u1EA7n d\xE2n A-m\xF4n \u0111\u1EEBng khi\xEAu kh\xEDch hay g\xE2y chi\u1EBFn v\u1EDBi h\u1ECD v\xEC ta s\u1EBD kh\xF4ng c\u1EA5p m\u1EA3nh \u0111\u1EA5t n\xE0o c\u1EE7a h\u1ECD cho c\xE1c ng\u01B0\u01A1i \u0111\xE2u. Ta \u0111\xE3 c\u1EA5p \u0111\u1EA5t \u1EA5y cho con ch\xE1u L\xF3t l\xE0m t\xE0i s\u1EA3n.\" "), mdx("h6", {
