  }, "v22"), mdx("p", null, "CH\xDAA c\u0169ng l\xE0m nh\u01B0 th\u1EBF cho d\xF2ng d\xF5i \xCA-sau s\u1ED1ng \u1EDF \xCA-\u0111\xF4m, khi Ng\xE0i ti\xEAu di\u1EC7t d\xE2n H\xF4-r\xEDt. Ng\u01B0\u1EDDi \xCA-\u0111\xF4m \u0111\xE1nh \u0111u\u1ED5i v\xE0 chi\u1EBFm l\u1EA5y \u0111\u1EA5t c\u1EE7a h\u1ECD v\xE0 sinh s\u1ED1ng \u1EDF \u0111\xF3 cho \u0111\u1EBFn ng\xE0y nay. "), mdx("h6", {
