    "id": "v33"
  }, "v33"), mdx("p", null, "nh\u01B0ng CH\xDAA l\xE0 Th\u01B0\u1EE3ng \u0110\u1EBF trao h\u1ECD v\xE0o tay ch\xFAng ta. Ch\xFAng ta \u0111\xE1nh b\u1EA1i vua, c\xE1c con trai c\xF9ng c\u1EA3 \u0111o\xE0n qu\xE2n c\u1EE7a vua. "), mdx("h6", {
