  }, "v36"), mdx("p", null, "Ch\xFAng ta \u0111\xE1nh b\u1EA1i th\xE0nh A-r\xF4-e g\u1EA7n ven h\u1ED1 \u1EA0c-n\xF4n, v\xE0 ch\xFAng ta \u0111\xE1nh b\u1EA1i th\u1ECB tr\u1EA5n trong h\u1ED1, cho \u0111\u1EBFn t\u1EADn Ghi-l\xEA-\xE1t. Kh\xF4ng th\u1ECB tr\u1EA5n n\xE0o qu\xE1 m\u1EA1nh \u0111\u1ED1i v\u1EDBi ch\xFAng ta, v\xEC CH\xDAA trao cho ch\xFAng ta t\u1EA5t c\u1EA3 c\xE1c th\xE0nh \u0111\xF3. "), mdx("h6", {
